---
/**
 * About Us
 * Learn more about Woorkeasy and our mission.
 */
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | Woorkeasy"
  description="Woorkeasy offers 30+ free online tools for images, PDFs, finance, and development. All browser-based, no upload, 100% free."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 text-center">
    <h1 class="display-xl text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">About Woorkeasy</h1>
    <p class="body-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-4">Free online tools for everyone, built for privacy and speed.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="space-y-8 body-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Woorkeasy was created with a simple mission: provide high-quality, free online tools that anyone can use without sacrificing privacy or convenience. We believe that essential productivity tools should be accessible to everyone, no sign-ups, no payments, no data collection.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">What We Offer</h2>
        <p>We provide 30+ free online tools across multiple categories:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Image Tools</strong> " Convert, compress, crop, rotate, watermark, and remove backgrounds from images.</li>
          <li><strong>PDF Tools</strong> " Merge, split, convert, and rotate PDF documents.</li>
          <li><strong>Finance Tools</strong> " Convert OFX, QFX, Excel, CSV, clean and format data, parse PDF bank statements, and auto-detect formats.</li>
          <li><strong>Developer Tools</strong> " Base64 encode/decode, URL encoder, JSON formatter, and more.</li>
          <li><strong>Utility Tools</strong> " Character counter, web page screenshot tool, and other handy utilities.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Privacy-First Approach</h2>
        <p>Every tool on Woorkeasy runs entirely in your browser. Your files never leave your device. We do not have servers that process or store your data. This client-side approach means your sensitive documents, financial data, and personal images remain private and secure.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Built on User Feedback</h2>
        <p>We build tools based on what our users need. If you have a suggestion for a new tool or an improvement to an existing one, we encourage you to reach out. Our roadmap is driven by user requests, and we regularly add new tools based on your feedback.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? Email us at <a href="mailto:woorkeasy@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">woorkeasy@gmail.com</a> or use the Request a Tool button on our homepage.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
